      "patch_summary": "This patch series improves the reclaim loop and dirty folio handling in the mm/mglru module, addressing issues related to memory cgroup (memcg) management and fairness. The changes aim to enhance the performance and efficiency of memory allocation and deallocation processes. The approach taken involves refining the existing code to better handle memory pressure and reclaiming, with a focus on improving the overall system responsiveness and stability."
